{"tid":2016214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook 被內容審查員集體控告 庭外和解賠償 5200 萬美元","createTime":"2020-05-14T08:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T10:07:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"978b1551eea0394bc9fb1cd7a5ee80332335d0e8","tid":2016214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"很多社交網站都設立審查機制，內容審查員就是負責審查和過濾，工作期間經常會接觸到暴力、虐待等內容。早前有內容審查員因受到心理創傷，而向 Facebook 提出集體控告；最終在近日達成庭外和解，Facebook 同意賠償 5200 萬美元（約港幣 4 億元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據前日（12 日）公布的庭外和解內容，Facebook 同意向每名內容審查員賠償最少 1000 美元（約港幣 7800 元）；若確診患上創傷後遺症（PTSD）等精神疾病，則最多可獲得額外 5 萬美元（約港幣 39 萬元）的賠償⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/14/facebook-contractors/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-contractors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F14%2Ffacebook-contractors%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Futm_source%3Drss%26utm_medium%3Drss%26utm_campaign%3Dfacebook-contractors&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7nGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=6b523d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/14/facebook-contractors/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-contractors</a>"},{"pid":"4427d82b6683d9668fc6ac18230b61bcc083979f","tid":2016214,"uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:41:36.000Z","msg":"賣下廣告 賣一班人資料 或者 敏感人士 都收返曬啦 先4億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f6b95f545f05a8d14ef83dfda2946aeba44810","tid":2016214,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"應該睇好多變態野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}